    "The previous section demonstrates that comparative assessment exhibits positional bias which may impact system decisions.",
    "We therefore investigate whether debiasing can improve evaluation performance.",
    "Table 6 shows standard and debiased LLM comparative assessment performance for the considered tasks and scores, with WebNLG SEM and Podcast omitted due to the required emergent ability and large context length respectively.",
    "We observe that debiasing can lead to performance boosts, where we note that the prompts which have a high bias (seen in Table 5 and Table 9 in the appendix) benefit most from debiasing."
